OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FSome brighter spells
OL,6,Finitially but turning wet and windy
OL,7,Ffrom the west through Thursday. Not as
OL,8,Fwarm, but still mild for the time of
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,12,Fwith further rain at times on Friday.
OL,13,FDrier and perhaps brighter on Saturday
OL,14,Fbefore further rain arrives later and
OL,15,Finto Sunday. Often windy with
OL,16,Ftemperatures returning to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
